title: Leonardo da Vinci Secreats - Android Puzzle Game
description:
Awesome puzzle game on Android "Leonardo da Vinci Secrets".
Main control: 1 click - change one fragment on another, double click - change fragment's angle.
Find more than 20 famous Leonardo da Vinci's pictures and for every next step you need to find key. 
Perfect game for adults and children, but not easy, because Leonardo's pictures not collored.
Have a good time in game!
